<item>
            <title>[LU-6032] no need to disable softirq for export:exp_rpc_lock</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-6032</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;it is not necessary to call ldlm_lock_busy() in timer callback, we can call it in thread context of expired_lock_main. With this change, we don&apos;t need to disable softirq anymore for export:exp_rpc_lock&lt;/p&gt;</description>
